    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for someone looking for a major project or a parts donor. The engine currently struggles to stay idling and there is a significant oil leak that will require immediate attention before any regular driving. The exterior has substantial rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please come prepared with a trailer, as the car is not currently reliable for long-distance travel.",
